<plot>When Roberto (Pritan Shrestha), a Spanish teenager, loses his parents and girlfriend in a car accident, he loses the will to live along with his eyesight. Thrown into the world of darkness, he has only his nanny, Cheryl (Roz McCutcheon), for support. She persuades him to get an eye transplant but Roberto does not agree his life is going to get better. But Cheryl has no way to make Roberto start living again and get his faith back so, she makes a bet with Roberto that will he find love again. Who will win the bet? Will Roberto ever find love again?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074619</url></doc>
